><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/18/02 2:46:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate Runner to be</span><hr size=1> yea its easy I did it yesterday.  Port up to PoH keep the wall on your right and stay midway up the wall until you get to the &quot;safespot&quot; or pull spot.  The maestro's r oom is two down from there and the book is above his room on a nightstand.  Oh yea go up naked drown yourself somewhere and after you get the book have a cleric revive you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usharafi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharafi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/18/02 6:03:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate Runner to be</span><hr size=1> <br>I did it cake with a Wizzy, drood, cleric and me ( Rog ) :P<br><br>Rog keels himself close to his bind point, wizzy dies in a dual.<br><br>Rogue Wizzy and drood grp up. Cleric sits looking at corpses :P<br><br>Rogue gets invis, As soon as wizzy ports Drood casts invis on wizzy and disbands.<br><br>When you arrive in sunny hate Both of you will be invis. Cleric then casts revive on wizzys corpse ( 10 min decay i think on duels ) and a invis wizzy poofs without having to become vis.<br><br>Rogue then makes his way to the wall and drops invis for sneak hide.<br><br>Then makes his way to do the deed. When book is obtained cleric rezes rogue. (3 hrs on a xp loss kill )<br><br>Personally i camped up there and logged in every 30 mins to see if it had popped.<br><br>Cake<br><br>Sharafi Lim'Dul 57 Templar &lt;Red Sky&gt;<br>Farkuu Soultaker 54 Reaver<br>Zebarti Lim'Dul 54 Rake &lt;Red SKy&gt;<br>Others Still In The Shadows.<br>Bertoxx <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ureztarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reztarn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/18/02 11:53:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate Runner to be</span><hr size=1> oooh revive...damn could have saved buying a gate potion for my crazy wizard friend.  I used a gate potion down because I stuffed up my rez box and the cleric was off raiding.  But good luck.  As I tell everyone &quot;Get a Shiny Brass Idol!&quot;  just in case you have to make a dash for the book it gives you 14 seconds to grab the book while getting pounded on <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br><br>Tizla <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usithen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sithen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 5:47:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sharafi's post</span><hr size=1> Thanks a ton for this post, I was really nervous about the zone in as my PC is fairly fast, but not rockin fast...  Having read how simple this sounds, I just gotta say this should be added to the Walk Through, but I guess I'll have to go try it first, that'll be tomorrow assuming I can find a wizzy to get me up there.  Thanks again Sharafi, very nice post, I'll let you know the results as soon as I'm done. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unightgod.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NightGod</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 9:58:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sharafi's post</span><hr size=1> For the record, once you rez a corpse (even a dueled one), it can be rezzed again an infinate number of times (with no extra exp gain) until the corpse decays. SO ya don't even have to worry about the 4% exp loss-just diein a duel, get a epic rez/revive and then you can be rezzed back to your corpse whenever... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usharafi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharafi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 8:38:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sharafi's post</span><hr size=1> <br>That has been changed i think, we tested it before i did my dash with a friend and i was unable to rez or revive him after 10-15 mins ( cant remember exactly ) it was after the patch where you could /con corpses and see the timer. The corpse had 2:50 odd to decay but was unable to be rezed/revived.<br><br>Might be fixed now but check before you go to hate and find it dosn't work <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Sharafi Lim'Dul 57 Templar &lt;Red Sky&gt;<br>Farkuu Soultaker 54 Reaver<br>Zebarti Lim'Dul 54 Rake &lt;Red Sky&gt;<br>Others Still In The Shadows.<br>Bertoxx <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4443.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4443.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4443.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=4443.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4443.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4443.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump t